<item>
            <title>[LU-6437] python-docutils/rst2man required even with --disable-doc</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6437</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;python-docutils is not available for all environments, including Intel MPSS. configuring with --disable-doc should negate it as a build requirement. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;rpmbuild  -&lt;del&gt;define &quot;configure_args  &apos;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;del&gt;disable-liblustre&apos; &apos;&lt;/del&gt;-disable-doc&apos;&quot; --define &quot;kdir /home/build/kernel/rpmbuild/BUILD/kernel-2.6.32.431.29.2.el6_lustre&quot; --define &quot;kobjdir /home/build/kernel/rpmbuild/BUILD/kernel-2.6.32.431.29.2.el6_lustre&quot; --define &quot;kmoddir extra&quot; -ta lustre-2.7.51.tar.gz&lt;br/&gt;
error: Failed build dependencies:&lt;br/&gt;
	python-docutils is needed by lustre-2.7.51-2.6.32.431.29.2.el6_lustre_g61787e1.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
make: *** &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;rpms&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Error 1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
